Review:
I went here for consultation for my cough.
The waiting period was about 15-20 mins.
The receptionist will take in your O2 level, BP measurement and weight. The doctor asked me for my symptoms, examined me and prescribed me with the required medication.
It is a nice small hospital.
The consultation fees was 150 Rs.
They have a dispensary right next to the hospital for access and you can find all prescribed medicines there.
In all it was a decent experience.
